hor-h4yM6-N0eITEQqfS6Lh1ag">Mao Trạch Đông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tu%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%ADu-cu%E1%BB%93ng-ng%C3%B4n-th%C3%B9-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Ti%C3%AAu-%C3%82n-nh%E1%BB%8B-hi%E1%BB%87p-lu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-9ZhJAi3DjT-FEtHvvFbdPw">Tuý hậu cuồng ngôn, thù tặng Tiêu, Ân nhị hiệp luật - 醉後狂言，酬贈蕭、殷二協律</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%B3-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-trung-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%C3%A1c-ti%C3%AAn-k%C3%BD-Nghi%C3%AAm-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%B4ng-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-JcBbnMT06mDuoToD3fziXQ">Tương phó Thành Đô thảo đường đồ trung hữu tác, tiên ký Nghiêm Trịnh công kỳ 3 - 將赴成都草堂途中有作，先寄嚴鄭公其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-Nh%C3%A2n/Xu%C3%A2n-kh%E1%BB%A9/poem-175X2AF_S_6_fxqTmamwcA">Xuân khứ - 春去</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-Nh%C3%A2n/author-lVq0c6nfaKZdZ1zJHdkYzA">Diệp Nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-V%C3%B5/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-v%C3%A3n-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-TbXxkinvtnHhyMCv98xBIA">Xuân nhật vãn vọng - 春日晚望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-V%C3%B5/author-MlgffkeJIL4Sf88n2ZEHoA">Mạnh Đại Võ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
